#: ../../src/guide/platform_nixos/statshost.rst:15
msgid ""
"A Telegraf daemon runs on all NixOS VMs. All metrics collected by "
"Telegraf are picked up by Prometheus. You can add custom inputs by "
"putting :file:`*.conf` files into :file:`/etc/local/telegraf`. Telegraf "
"configuration files are in the `TOML <https://github.com/toml-"
"lang/toml>`_ format. See the `Telegraf configuration page "
"<https://github.com/influxdata/telegraf/blob/master/docs/CONFIGURATION.md>`_"
" for details. The available inputs are `documented separately "
"<https://github.com/influxdata/telegraf/tree/master/plugins/inputs>`_."
msgstr ""

